chnical novelty in this paper is that\nthe methodology used draws from three (largely separate) sources: probability\ntheory, functional Hilbert spaces, and the approximation theory of bounded\noperators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Nov 2018 13:16:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-15"}
